relation: Make sure defhistogram, defcounter, deftimer and so on quote metric titles Without this change, defhistogram and friends won't compile. Currently desugared-title returns the name as a list of 3 strings, which needs to be quoted for things to compile: ("test" "group" "ubermetric") will be evaluated without quoting.
Cherry pick metrics.meters/count, fixes #9 Contributed by Ian Eure.
Move the ring repo into this one.
